<figureCitation box="[134,262,1491,1517]" captionStart="APPENDIX" captionStartId="51.[132,144,964,982]" captionTargetPageId="51" captionText="APPENDIX 7. — Measurements of teleoconch and protoconch of Benthonellania aequatorialis (Thiele, 1925) n. comb. in mm, with range,mean and standard deviation: 1, 2, Nias-Sudkanal 470 m depth (‘subadult’)." pageId="25" pageNumber="358">Appendix 7</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
