<subSubSection pageId="25" pageNumber="358" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="25.[130,776,1555,2028]" box="[132,232,1555,1581]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">REMARKS</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="25.[130,776,1555,2028]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">
<taxonomicName authority="Thiele, 1925" authorityName="Thiele" authorityYear="1925" box="[132,481,1586,1613]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Rissoa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="aequatorialis">
<emphasis box="[132,336,1586,1612]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">Rissoa aequatorialis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Thiele" box="[344,481,1586,1613]" firstAuthor="Thiele" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" pagination="35 - 382" refId="ref34767" refString="THIELE J. 1925. - Gastropoden der Deutschen Tiefsee-Expedition. II Teil. Wissenschaftliche Ergebnisse der Deutschen TiefseeExpedition auf dem Dampfer &quot; Valdivia &quot; 1898 - 1899: 17 (2): 35 - 382, pls 13 - 46 [reprints paginated 1 - 348, pls 1 - 34]." type="journal article" year="1925">Thiele, 1925</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was dubitatively suggested by 
<bibRefCitation author="Lozouet" box="[168,340,1618,1645]" firstAuthor="Lozouet" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" pagination="313 - 328" refId="ref33972" refString="LOZOUET P. 1990. - Benthonellania nouveau genre de Rissoidae (Gastropoda, Prosobranchia) du bathyal atlantique. Bulletin du Museum national d'Histoire naturelle (section A Zoologie) (4) 12: 313 - 328." type="journal article" year="1990">Lozouet (1990)</bibRefCitation>
to belong in his new genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lozouet" authorityYear="1990" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">Benthonellania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see also 
<bibRefCitation author="Hasegawa" box="[292,526,1650,1677]" firstAuthor="Hasegawa" page="152" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" pagination="137 - 190" refId="ref33765" refString="HASEGAWA K. 2005. - A Preliminary List of Deep-Sea Gastropods Collected from the Nansei Islands, Southwestern Japan. National Science Museum Monographs 29: 137 - 190." type="journal article" year="2005">Hasegawa 2005: 152</bibRefCitation>
). Based on the current systematic framework, we agree and propose 
<taxonomicName authority="(Thiele, 1925)" authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Thiele" baseAuthorityYear="1925" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="aequatorialis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">Benthonellania aequatorialis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Thiele" box="[282,423,1714,1741]" firstAuthor="Thiele" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" pagination="35 - 382" refId="ref34767" refString="THIELE J. 1925. - Gastropoden der Deutschen Tiefsee-Expedition. II Teil. Wissenschaftliche Ergebnisse der Deutschen TiefseeExpedition auf dem Dampfer &quot; Valdivia &quot; 1898 - 1899: 17 (2): 35 - 382, pls 13 - 46 [reprints paginated 1 - 348, pls 1 - 34]." type="journal article" year="1925">Thiele, 1925</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
as new combination for 
<taxonomicName authority="Thiele, 1925" authorityName="Thiele" authorityYear="1925" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Rissoa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="aequatorialis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">Rissoa aequatorialis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Thiele" box="[272,411,1746,1773]" firstAuthor="Thiele" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" pagination="35 - 382" refId="ref34767" refString="THIELE J. 1925. - Gastropoden der Deutschen Tiefsee-Expedition. II Teil. Wissenschaftliche Ergebnisse der Deutschen TiefseeExpedition auf dem Dampfer &quot; Valdivia &quot; 1898 - 1899: 17 (2): 35 - 382, pls 13 - 46 [reprints paginated 1 - 348, pls 1 - 34]." type="journal article" year="1925">Thiele, 1925</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="25.[130,776,1555,2028]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Thiele" baseAuthorityYear="1925" box="[155,439,1778,1804]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="aequatorialis" status="n. comb.">
<emphasis box="[155,439,1778,1804]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">Benthonellania aequatorialis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[444,536,1778,1804]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" rank="species">n. comb.</taxonomicNameLabel>
differs from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Thiele" baseAuthorityYear="1925" box="[665,775,1778,1804]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="africana" status="n. comb.">
<emphasis box="[665,775,1778,1804]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">B. africana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[132,228,1810,1836]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" rank="species">n. comb.</taxonomicNameLabel>
in its multispiral, spirally sculptured protoconch vs paucispiral and smooth in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Thiele" baseAuthorityYear="1925" box="[416,531,1842,1868]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="africana" status="n. comb.">
<emphasis box="[416,531,1842,1868]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">B. africana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[537,636,1841,1868]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" rank="species">n. comb.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, and the lack of spiral cordlets on the base, present in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Thiele" baseAuthorityYear="1925" box="[559,673,1874,1900]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="africana" status="n. comb.">
<emphasis box="[559,673,1874,1900]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">B. africana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[680,776,1873,1900]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" rank="species">n. comb.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="25.[130,776,1555,2028]" lastBlockId="25.[812,1455,885,1070]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">
As already noticed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Hasegawa" box="[382,566,1905,1932]" firstAuthor="Hasegawa" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" pagination="137 - 190" refId="ref33765" refString="HASEGAWA K. 2005. - A Preliminary List of Deep-Sea Gastropods Collected from the Nansei Islands, Southwestern Japan. National Science Museum Monographs 29: 137 - 190." type="journal article" year="2005">Hasegawa (2005)</bibRefCitation>
a juvenile specimen of an unidentified 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lozouet" authorityYear="1990" box="[332,489,1937,1963]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[332,489,1937,1963]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">Benthonellania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from southwestern 
<collectingCountry box="[706,769,1938,1964]" name="Japan" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">Japan</collectingCountry>
, recalls 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Thiele" baseAuthorityYear="1925" box="[202,495,1969,1995]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="aequatorialis" status="n. comb.">
<emphasis box="[202,495,1969,1995]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">Benthonellania aequatorialis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[500,594,1969,1996]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" rank="species">n. comb.</taxonomicNameLabel>
(Hasegawa: 152, fig. 5J). However, that specimen quite probably represents a distinct, undescribed species, differing from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Thiele" baseAuthorityYear="1925" box="[1292,1455,885,911]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="aequatorialis" status="n. comb.">
<emphasis box="[1292,1455,885,911]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">B. aequatorialis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[813,911,917,943]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" rank="species">n. comb.</taxonomicNameLabel>
by its wider base and more angled periphery, and the faint spiral sculpture on the base (absent in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Thiele" baseAuthorityYear="1925" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="aequatorialis" status="n. comb.">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">B. aequatorialis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[871,972,980,1007]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" rank="species">n. comb.</taxonomicNameLabel>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="25.[812,1455,885,1070]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">
See under 
<taxonomicName authority="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio, 2022" authorityName="Amati &amp; Giulio &amp; Oliverio" authorityYear="2022" box="[946,1180,1012,1038]" class="Gastropoda" family="Rissoidae" genus="Benthonellania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="bouteti" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[946,1180,1012,1038]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="358">Benthonellania bouteti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1185,1242,1013,1039]" pageId="25" pageNumber="358" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
for diagnostic comparison.
</paragraph>
